        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're notorious for your discipline to the point that you can leverage your fame to ask favors of fans and colleagues. You can use the Lore skill that you gain from @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Voracious Reader] to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Gather Information]. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Diplomacy checks to [[/act make-an-impression]] on people interested in your chosen discipline. If you're legendary in the Lore skill, this circumstance bonus increases to +4.</p>"
